These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, hip-hop
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is not to the right of the fan of hip-hop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | martial-arts |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: rat, cat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
3. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | rat | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, tram
1. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | taxi | tram |

 #################################

 
